content: On the plane back to NYC, watching Japan shrink beneath the clouds. It's surreal how one place can change you so deeply in such a short time.

content: Back in NYC. The skyline feels different now, like I'm seeing it with new eyes. Makes me think about how our experiences shape our perception.
